{"tid":1468323,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"過左兩日，我仲係好傷心","createTime":"2019-08-13T18:21:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T18:32:03.000Z","uid":69242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cc78aed7ad5c8ef4825441d8fc879ef734d7f782","tid":1468323,"uid":69242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:21:18.000Z","msg":"個女仔比人射爆眼球，林鄭叫佢報警，叫佢早日康復，人地成粒眼球都冇埋，一世盲左、毀容，叫一個永久失明嘅人早日康復？你要死趁早啦！<br />\n成粒布袋彈插入去護目鏡度仲要調查？調查幾耐？兩年三年四年呀？<br />\n射盲個女仔果個係咩人我知你知，叫個女仔向兇手報案？！屌你滷味啦！林鄭！<br />\n<br />\n無論係咩派別，我相信每人都有良知，都會為呢位少女哭泣，希望大家能夠明白呢位少女當初出黎嘅原因，並唔係要打交，並唔係要同人嘈交，而係同二百萬個香港市民一樣，希望政府聆聽市民嘅聲音，爭取五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n唔好比仇恨蒙蔽，更加唔好放棄，要匯聚大家嘅力量，繼續爭取五大訴求"},{"pid":"77ad40845f5d294fa7f483bec471f6e4bb138cd5","tid":1468323,"uid":60049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:24:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5gr4M4s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5gr4M4s.jpg&h=63cfee4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">Credit: @seztomimi</span>"},{"pid":"d4db74568cbe3279c5a5d6d5d665415810886022","tid":1468323,"uid":285481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:28:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1FNfTAU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1FNfTAU.jpg&h=7becab2d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E9TyFfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE9TyFfU.jpg&h=0b41b5ed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8shGO9f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8shGO9f.jpg&h=e0856b12&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"97a32320860f7192584dd05cec2e0cdbbe506960","tid":1468323,"uid":69242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:32:03.000Z","msg":"我睇完一次個條片之後，都冇勇氣完整睇多一次，畫面實在教人太心酸，點解警察要用到槍去奪去佢嘅眼睛，令佢一世都睇唔到野、毀容，點解政府要咁殘忍對付香港市民，點解政